{"tid":1069793,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱有條毒撚it狗揼咗人盒飯落垃圾桶","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T08:09:34.000Z","uid":135638,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7e940a52baa413cd745f7bf04c91c48a5f22be","tid":1069793,"uid":135638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"話説啱啱lunch time 我喺房到睇緊youtube<br />\n點知突然間聽到出面有人喺到嘈<br />\n聽把聲應該又係新請嚟嘅毒撚it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條毒撚請咗返嚟一個月<br />\n日日都好似有狂燥症咁喺到細細聲屌鬼<br />\n黑口黑面好似成間公司都得罪佢咁<br />\n成面暗瘡仲戴紅框眼鏡<br />\n返工仲夠擔揹嗰啲動漫女女索袋返嚟<br />\n驚死人唔知佢係毒撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時我都睇佢唔順眼<br />\n啲同事都怕撚咗佢<br />\n<br />\n點知出面嘈完之後<br />\n有同事入我房話返我聽發生咩事<br />\n原來條毒撚夠擔死揼人飯盒落垃圾桶<br />\n仲要屌返人轉頭<br />\n<br />\n我嬲撚到即刻叫條毒撚入房<br />\n叫佢抖返兩日<br />\n佢仲口噏噏話「仲好 可以陪下老婆」<br />\n屌你老母你條油頭毒撚撚有老婆咩<br />\n而家搞緊手續炒鳩條廢柴<br />\n屌 又要請過人<br />\n而家啲毒撚真係好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5ffce6a842452f9bc5bb02bc2a8c4e6601710b","tid":1069793,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd89c2a3c4666e6cc683c95cfd1b6aafe93d9a87","tid":1069793,"uid":135638,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3c5ffce6a842452f9bc5bb02bc2a8c4e6601710b","tid":1069793,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"你就係條毒撚？<br />\n咁快放假放到悶？<br />\n有排你放呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb59d4e531fa5979d9a3c65dc9e57857466f6856","tid":1069793,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debb252a4409c2a936c02d2d7865e1de8d5fea54","tid":1069793,"uid":135638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb59d4e531fa5979d9a3c65dc9e57857466f6856","tid":1069793,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家啲毒撚真係好低質<br />\n好心佢哋學下我哋連登手足啦"}]}